Project Name: UniMatch.

Main Idea: A platform that connects students seeking specialized academic support with unemployed PhD researchers looking for flexible teaching opportunities.

2. Objective of the Site

For Students: Providing an easy-to-use platform that enables them to find specialized tutors to support them academically.

For Teachers: Providing a flexible teaching opportunity with a financial income that helps them in their academic journey.

